ed2kLC - the ed2k Link Converter is a simple GUI program for convert ed2k 
link between without tag, HTML tag and BBcode tag that we usually post it 
on the forum and web. The ed2k Link Converter also can convert ed2k link 
between useing UTF-8 (ex: %E4%B8%AD) format and Unicode / MBCS that you can 
see it clearly (ex: ¤¤). You can run it on Unix-like system and Windows.

In this Program, you'll see those file:
  ed2klc.py:
    The main entry point that will call ed2klcGUI.py

  ed2klcGUI.py:
    The GUI part. This file contain all of GUI unit.

  ed2kConvert.py:
    The Converter part. It can be an independent module.

  ed2klc.ico:
    The program's icon.

How to use?
first, you have to check that your computer is already install python 2.x
(python 2.6 is recommend), and than, run ed2klc.py. If ed2klc.py is runing
correctly, you will see an GUI.
After that, insert ed2k link(s) into input text area and click 'Convert'
button, if the link(s) that you insert is/are legal, you will see a dialog
notify you convert finished and you can see the converted link in converted
text area. If you insert an illegal ed2k file link, it will stop convert
directly and you can't see the converted link in converted text area.
You can clean input & converted link area with click 'Clean' Button.